target_text: It\u2019s a solid piece of work that answers questions people have been asking,\u201d Julie Fischer, a microbiologist at Georgetown University who was not involved in the study, tells the AP. \u201cWhat we need to be doing is washing our hands, being aware that people who are infected may be contaminating surfaces,\u201d and not touching our faces
